    "500104": {
        "Desc": "Watch the opening ceremony",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "The Pilgrimage of the Return of the Sacred Flame is a competition with a long, storied history. Countless hopefuls have gathered here today, each vying for the same prize — the right to serve their homeland in the Night Warden Wars."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Before we begin, allow me to remind everyone of the rules. Today's tournament begins with the team stage, before advancing into individual competition."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Each team will board a hot-air balloon, which will land at a random location."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Contestants must search for Fire Towers within the contest grounds, accumulate Contending Fire through combat, and bring a sufficient amount back to the Stadium."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Defeat in combat, departure from the contest grounds, and running out of time all lead to elimination! Only the strongest teams will be able to withstand the onslaught of battle and return to the arena, blazing Fire in hand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Only those who emerge triumphant in the team stage earn the right to take part in the individual battles. The outcome of these one-on-one matches not only affects the contestants' individual scores but also determines their next opponent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "After many rounds of battle, the contestants with the top five rankings will get the chance to take part in the Night Warden Wars!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Now, let us welcome our Archon as she delivers the opening address!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Skill, strategy, fortune, form... Many factors influence strength, but victory never lies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "The Pilgrimage is not merely a trial to determine the strongest among us, but also a stage upon which to showcase your individual growth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Today marks the beginning of yet another legendary saga — one written in the triumphs of the victors! So, without further ado... Let the games begin!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, that's the Pyro Archon!? Is it just Paimon, or does she seem kinda intimidating...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Kachina said she was \"friendly and welcoming,\" but, uh... how did she come to that conclusion?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "She does seem pretty imposing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Didn't Kachina say she was just an ordinary person before becoming the Archon? Sure doesn't seem like it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "She doesn't seem ordinary at all... Ooh, look, it's Kachina and the others!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to talk to her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, but it would be kinda rude to bother her during the Pilgrimage, don't you think?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We should wait for a better time... Ooh, look! It's Kachina and the others!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Well, folks, it's clear the contestants are already raring to go! The teams will now board their hot-air balloons and make their way to the competition grounds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mersa",
                    "T": "Chasca! Chasca!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zacatula",
                    "T": "Go, Chasca! You can do it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teayo",
                    "T": "Kick their butts, Itzna!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sausa",
                    "T": "Go, Mualani! Go!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You can do it, Kachina!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "And the crowd goes wiiild! The hot-air balloons are about to ascend — contestants, prepare yourselves to take flight!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Remember the rules! The balloons will take you to random locations, and your battle starts the moment you land. Best your competition, collect Sacred Fire, and bring it back to the Stadium."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Balam",
                    "T": "Good luck, everyone!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
