    "500110": {
        "Desc": "Complete the team stage",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "Congratulations, Mualani! Congratulations, Kachina! You've successfully cleared the team stage!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mersa",
                    "T": "Amazing! Congratulations!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Taenga",
                    "T": "Congratulations!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sausa",
                    "T": "Keep it up, Mualani!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zacatula",
                    "T": "Kachina! Mualani!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Kachina! Mualani!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Kachina! Mualani!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lamanai",
                    "T": "You two can take a short break while the team stage comes to a close. We'll draw names to determine the individual match-ups in a moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lamanai",
                    "T": "After that, we'll proceed to the next stage of the competition. I wish you both the best."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "You two are assigned to different lounge areas. If you'll follow me, please, Kachina."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Solo battles next, and I was three wins short last time. I've got to do better."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Phew... Just calm down, Kachina. You're in good form. You can do this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "Hold it right there. This is the contestants' lounge. Unauthorized access is prohibited."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tepexpan",
                    "T": "We're contestants, too! Let us through!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "According to my list, you're not among the individual match contenders, nor are you related to any of the remaining candidates."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tepexpan",
                    "T": "Well, we'd still be candidates if it was just based on strength! We only lost because two other contestants snuck up on us like cowards! If you could just go contact the referee, we'll wait right here for you to—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tamuin",
                    "T": "Ah..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Wait, you two are..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tepexpan",
                    "T": "Well, look who we have here. Remember us? Your little trick got us disqualified!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tamuin",
                    "T": "Since we've crossed paths again, let's settle this once and for all. We'll see who truly deserves to advance to the next stage... Fight us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Right now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "Don't mind him, Kachina. Tournament rules place you under no obligation to honor that request — a loss is a loss, and that's final."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "You! Don't just stand there! Get security over here, now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tepexpan",
                    "T": "Forget the rules! Isn't the Pilgrimage about picking the strongest warriors? She just happened to catch us off-guard. It was all luck!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tamuin",
                    "T": "Exactly. Now's our chance to duke it out fair and square—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Kachina!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm happy to oblige..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tepexpan",
                    "T": "Who are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}! Paimon! What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We just came to have a chat, and then all of a sudden, these guys were threatening you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph. You're not bullying Kachina on our watch!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Th—Thanks, you guys."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "I don't know your names... But, if you really want to face me, I'll allow it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "It has to wait until after the tournament, though! I need to focus on the upcoming matches. I don't want to let my parents down, or any of the friends who helped me get this far."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "That's enough, you two. \"Being caught off-guard\" is not an excuse. You think you can cry foul play when you face the Abyss?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "If this behavior persists, you may find yourselves barred from future competition."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tamuin",
                    "T": "Tch... Whatever. Let's go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are you alright? You're not hurt anywhere, are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "No, thanks to you. To be honest, I totally blanked out just now. I had no idea what to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's alright. Just relax."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Focus on your upcoming matches."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Right! I—I'll show them what I'm made of!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That sounds more like it! You can do it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lamanai",
                    "T": "I heard there was trouble... Has the situation been resolved?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tonina",
                    "T": "Yes. It was nothing out of the ordinary — a couple of sore losers coming to stir up trouble with the contestants."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lamanai",
                    "T": "*sigh* Some people are so obsessed with glory, they can't even bear the idea of failure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lamanai",
                    "T": "I hope you don't let them get to you, Kachina, because you'll need to get ready. Your match is up soon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "That came up quick... Alright, I'm coming!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Hehe, w—well, guess I'm off!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
