    "500210": {
        "Desc": "Deal with the unforeseen situation",
        "Step": "And here you thought that you could catch a few beauty winks after fixing that abandoned hot spring, but a fierce battle has broken out in the dead of night. What in the world happened?",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "To arms, everyone! To arms!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hikueru",
                    "T": "Ugh, why now!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*snore*... Huh? What's with all the noise...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, Paimon, wake up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Mualani? What's going on... Ahhh, where did all these monsters come from!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "It's the Abyss. Our patrols are trying to drive them back as we speak."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Come with me. I'll take you somewhere safe!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Taheta",
                    "T": "Mualani, a little help over here? We can't hold 'em back much longer!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "One moment. I'll be right there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'll come, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Really? That's perfect! I've been waiting for the chance to fight by your side!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's show those creatures what we're made of."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Couldn't have said it better myself!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Hang in there, we're here to help!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "500211": {
        "Desc": "Repel the Abyss incursion",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "500212": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Mualani",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "We've cleared out most of the monsters over here. Thanks for your help — it would've taken me ages on my own."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Looks like we're still in for a long night, though. We still have no idea where these creatures are coming from..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Let's go ask Amina. She'll have a better handle on the situation."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "500213": {
        "Desc": "Go with Mualani to find Amina",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Amina!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amina",
                    "T": "Oh, It's you three... Thank you for helping clear out all those monsters."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amina",
                    "T": "We were prepared for an attack, but we didn't have enough people to prevent them from breaking through our defenses. No casualties so far, though."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Where'd they come from this time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amina",
                    "T": "The east side. We've pinpointed the position of an Abyssal Pylon, but we don't have enough manpower to take it down."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "An Abyssal Pylon? What's that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "A kind of \"gate\" created by the Abyss, one that allows monsters from the Night Kingdom to enter the physical world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "The only way to end the attack is to destroy the Pylon as soon as possible. Otherwise, the endless hordes of monsters will exhaust our defenses."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amina",
                    "T": "Exactly, that's what I'm most concerned about. Their numbers suggest there might even be multiple Pylons in the area. We're searching for them as we speak..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "#Alright, we'll go seal off the one to the east. {NICKNAME}, Paimon, can I count on your help again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Of course! We can't just sit back and do nothing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amina",
                    "T": "On behalf of the People of the Springs, you have my thanks. We're counting on you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mualani",
                    "T": "Let's go, there's no time to lose. Take care, Amina."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
